The paper deals with image translation using a deep learning approach, specifically conditional Generative Adversarial Networks (cGAN). This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. The use of cGANs also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with remote sensing and satellite imagery, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) category.
